freenet.support
Class LimitedRangeIntByteArrayMap

java.lang.Object
  freenet.support.LimitedRangeIntByteArrayMap

public class LimitedRangeIntByteArrayMap
extends Object

Author:
amphibian A list of integers linked to byte[]'s. We keep a minimum and maximum of the integers. The integers are expected to be reasonably close together, and there is a maximum range. We provide a mechanism to sleep until the given packet number will no longer exceed the maximum range (which can be interrupted).
